About this item

  • EXTRA CLEAN "A" GRADE NATURAL WOOD VENEER EDGING Highest grade veneer quality unglued , fleeced back and sanded wood veneer edging for repair or enhancing cabinetry, furniture, DIY projects, shelving, crafts and more. Finely sanded to perfection, this plywood edge banding provides a perfect finish to your projects
  • NON GLUED WITH ULTRA SMOOTH SANDED FINISH Unglued edge banding made with top-quality "A" Grade wood veneer and German machinery, our veneer edge banding is top quality, made to be used in high quality projects. Our unglued edgebanding can be applied with contact cement adhesive for a strong, permanent bond
  • EASY APPLICATION This product doesnt have adhesive and can be applied manually by hand or with an automatic edgebander for our industrial customers. For manual hand application it is recommended to use contact cement adhesive. A two sided PSA peel and stick pressure sensitive adhesive tape can also be used, which is sold separately in our catalog. Our edge banding is available in a wide range of widths and length.
  • PREMIUM QUALITY REAL WOOD VENEER EDGING this veneer roll is all prepared ready for your application. Finely sanded to perfection, this plywood edge banding can be trimmed if required or lightly sanded down to fit.
  • USE ON A VARIETY OF SURFACES this roll of edge banding can be stained or painted with a lacquer finish to match your project. Suitable for a wide variety of surfaces, this veneer edging is great when applied to wood, plywood, particle board, hardboard or metal

Product Description

High quality wood veneer edge banding

Wood edge banding is used to cover the exposed sides of materials such as particle board, plywood, metal or MDF. The veneer edging increases the durability of your project as well as giving it a perfect finish.

Real wood unglued edge banding

Our wood edge banding is unglued with a German fleece paper back that provides a strong, durable and flexible product. This is the ideal product to cover edges and other surfaces. It is a very durable and long lasting bond. This product doesnt have adhesive and can be applied manually by hand or with an automatic edgebander for our industrial customers. You will receive a roll of wood veneer edging with your purchase.

Easy to install plywood edge banding

For manual hand application it is recommended to use contact cement adhesive. A two sided PSA peel and stick pressure sensitive adhesive tape can also be used, which is sold separately in our catalog. When choosing edgebanding widths, it is best to use a size that is slightly over the size that needs to be covered, although it is possible to use the exact size, but can be difficult to align with the edge or other surface. Also, we have a very popular and handy edgeband trimmer tool specially designed for trimming the edge

BUY NOW and complete your furniture and cabinetry edging with this premium quality, unglued wood veneer edging


WARNING: Californias Proposition 65

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Important Information

Proposition 65 Warning for California Consumers

WARNING: Drilling, sawing, sanding or machining wood products can expose you to wood dust, a substance known to the State of California to cause cancer. Avoid inhaling wood dust or use a dust mask or other safeguards for personal protection. For more information go to www.P65Warnings.ca.gov/wood
